/* eslint-disable react/prop-types */
import React, { Component } from "react"
import { Link, withRouter } from "react-router-dom"
import NavButton from "../Yang/components/Button"
import { Wrap, Left, Right, Item } from "./styles/navbar"

class Navbar extends Component {
  render() {
    // eslint-disable-next-line react/prop-types
    const { location } = this.props
    return (
      <Wrap>
        <Left activeKey={location.pathname}>
          <Link to="/">
            <Item href="/">BestTraveller</Item>
          </Link>
          <Link to="/">
            <Item className={location.pathname === "/home" && "active"}>
              Home
            </Item>
          </Link>
          <Link to="/packages">
            <Item className={location.pathname === "/packages" && "active"}>
              Packages
            </Item>
          </Link>
          <Link to="/about-us">
            <Item className={location.pathname === "/about" && "active"}>
              About us
            </Item>
          </Link>
          <Link to="/contact-us">
            <Item className={location.pathname === "/contact" && "active"}>
              Contact us
            </Item>
          </Link>
        </Left>
        <Right>
          <NavButton />
        </Right>
      </Wrap>
    )
  }
}

export default withRouter(Navbar)
